CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772287406
OL,3,CCornish brewery that makes Doom Bar to
OL,4,Cclose with the loss of 50 jobs
OL,6,FThe American owners of Sharp's Brewery
OL,7,F- who produce the UK's best selling
OL,8,Fcask ale - has announced it is to
OL,9,Fclose their site at Rock by the end of
OL,10,F2026 with the loss of 50 jobs.
OL,12,FMolson Coors Beverage Company has
OL,13,Fowned the Sharps brand for the past 15
OL,14,Fyears. Its popular brand Doom Bar,
OL,15,Fwhich is named after a dangerous
OL,16,Fsandbank at the mouth of the Camel
OL,17,FEstuary, has been brewed in Cornwall
OL,18,Fsince 1995.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
