OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772287406
OL,3,CCornish brewery that makes Doom Bar to
OL,4,Cclose with the loss of 50 jobs
OL,6,FThe company says the proposal, which
OL,7,Fis subject to consultation, is because
OL,8,Fof an 'evolving market' and is also
OL,9,Fpart of a wider cost savings plan
OL,10,Facross the UK and Ireland.
OL,12,FThe proposals will result in 200
OL,13,Fredundancies across the UK and Ireland.
OL,15,FThe company says it has explored every
OL,16,Falternative option to make the site at
OL,17,FRock financially sustainable in the
OL,18,Flong term before making the decision
OL,19,Fto close.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772287406
OL,3,CCornish brewery that makes Doom Bar to
OL,4,Cclose with the loss of 50 jobs
OL,6,FMolson Coors bought the brewery in
OL,7,F2011 and says since then it has
OL,8,Finvested more than #20 million to
OL,9,Fexpand capacity, upgrade equipment,
OL,10,Fsupport innovation and strengthen the
OL,11,FSharp's portfolio.
OL,13,FSimon Kerry, Managing Director, UK &
OL,14,FIreland at Molson Coors, said: "The
OL,15,Fproposed closure of Sharp's Brewery
OL,16,Fhas not been an easy decision for us
OL,17,Fto make. It has been a significant
OL,18,Fpart of our UK business for 15 years,
OL,19,Fwith an exceptional and committed team
OL,20,Fwho take such huge pride in their
OL,21,Fcraft.
OL,26,@vD@`OU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772287406
OL,3,CCornish brewery that makes Doom Bar to
OL,4,Cclose with the loss of 50 jobs
OL,6,F"We have invested significantly in the
OL,7,Fsite and the Sharp's brands over that
OL,8,Ftime and have taken every step we can
OL,9,Fto try and avoid this outcome.
OL,10,FHowever, the site is no longer
OL,11,Ffinancially sustainable as part of our
OL,12,Fnational production network.
OL,14,F"Our focus now is on supporting our
OL,15,FRock-based colleagues in every way we
OL,16,Fcan throughout this process."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
