OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772287406
OL,3,CCornish brewery that makes Doom Bar to
OL,4,Cclose with the loss of 50 jobs
OL,6,FThe company says it remains committed
OL,7,Fto the Sharp's brands and is currently
OL,8,Fexploring a number of alternative
OL,9,Fproduction routes, including the
OL,10,Fpossibility of producing them in
OL,11,Fpartnership.
OL,13,FSharp's Brewery was started in 1994 by
OL,14,FBill Sharp in a building which had
OL,15,Fpreviously been used to store
OL,16,Fspeedboats.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
